Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.54,0:06:27.48,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Please let go! You're going to \Ngive people the wrong idea!}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.48,0:06:29.78,Main,Reporter,0,0,0,,{Please! It's just for the Internet!}Làm ơn đi! Đang phát sóng đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:33.72,Main,Reporter,0,0,0,,{We've got next to no subscribers! \NWe barely get any views anyway!}Bọn này chẳng có ai theo dõi!\N Thoi thóp được vài người xem!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:35.62,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Doesn't it hurt you to say that?!}Tự nói thế không thấy đau lòng hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:38.98,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I guess we don't have a choice.}Có vẻ không còn cách nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:41.27,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Just for a little while, okay?}Chỉ một chút thôi nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:43.08,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{S-Senpai?!}C-Chị?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.08,0:06:45.82,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{And we're only going to be pretending.}Và chúng tôi chỉ đang giả vờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.82,0:06:51.59,Main - Top,Reporter,0,0,0,,{Thank you so much! Thank you \Nso, so much! Thank you!}Cảm ơn rất nhiều! May quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.85,0:06:51.88,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Pretending to be dating... Senpai...}Mình... giả vờ hẹn hò với chị ấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.67,0:06:55.38,Main,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{Okay, right where you are, please.}Rồi, xin mời hai người.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.82,0:06:59.24,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Pretending to be going out... \NSenpai's so mature.}Giả vờ hẹn hò... Chị ấy trưởng thành quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.24,0:07:01.33,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I must be the only one freaking out...}Chỉ có mình là hoảng loạn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:08.84,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I thought that agreeing to this would be \Neasier than getting her to give up, but...}Mình đã nghĩ đồng ý để con bé từ bỏ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.41,0:07:12.89,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Wh-What do couples even do?!}N-Nhưng cặp đôi phải làm gì?
