Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:14.16,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\b1\fscx120\fs28\c&H000000&\an6\bord0\shad0\fsp4\pos(221.334,184)}{Never had a\Nboyfriend}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.13,0:07:19.87,Main - Top,Shiori,0,0,0,,{If we're a couple, that would mean that \NI'm Shinozaki-san's girlfriend...}Nếu là cặp đôi, tức là mình là bạn gái Shinozaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:25.29,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fntimes new roman\b1\fscx120\fs20\c&H000000&\an6\bord0\shad0\fsp4\pos(188,184)}{Never had a\Nboyfriend}12 năm \Nkhông có bồ
