Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:23.86,Main - Top,Shiori,0,0,0,,{In other words, Shinozaki-san \Nis my boyfriend...}Nói cách khách, Shinozaki là bạn trai...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.28,0:07:29.18,Main,Reporter,0,0,0,,{And here we are! \NLet's start with the girlfriend.}Và bắt đầu thôi! Người bạn gái trước!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.18,0:07:30.77,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{S-Sure!}À vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.77,0:07:33.22,Main,Reporter,0,0,0,,{Tell us what you like about your boyfriend.}Hãy nói tôi nghe điểm tốt của anh ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:35.48,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{What I like...?}Điểm tốt á...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.13,0:07:39.49,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{This is kinda embarrassing, \Nbut I can take it...}Cái này hơi xấu hổ nhưng chỉ thế thôi thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:45.44,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I like how serious he is, and how he really \Nthrows himself into the tasks he's given.}Tôi thích dáng vẻ chăm chỉ và cố gắng của anh ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:48.64,Main,Reporter,0,0,0,,{That sounds lovely!}Tuyệt thật đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.64,0:07:51.03,Main,Reporter,0,0,0,,{You two met on the job?}Hai người quen nhau ở chỗ làm ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:51.97,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:55.12,Main,Reporter,0,0,0,,{So, you must've gotten to know \Neach other while working.}Vậy là quen nhau trong khi làm việc nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:56.32,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Chính xác.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.03,0:07:59.41,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{This doesn't seem so hard, after all.}Chỉ thế này thì đơn giản.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:02.09,Main,Reporter,0,0,0,,{Now, next, let's see...}Vậy thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.42,0:08:04.95,Main,Reporter,0,0,0,,{What was your first kiss like? And where?}Nụ hôn đầu ở đâu? Và cảm xúc như nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:07.23,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Hold on a second!}Khoan đã!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:10.52,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Isn't that raising the \Nbar a little suddenly?!}Tự nhiên tăng độ khó thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.52,0:08:12.41,Main,Reporter,0,0,0,,{Huh? You think?}Hả? Thế á?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.41,0:08:16.96,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{We're only pretending to be a couple, \Nso questions that are too probing might be...}Chị đang giả vờ thôi mà, và câu hỏi đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:22.33,Main,Reporter,0,0,0,,{Now, now, just imagine what \Nyou wish it'd be like!}Thôi nào, cứ tưởng tượng ra cũng được.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.12,0:08:25.15,Main,Reporter,0,0,0,,{Please? Please? Please...?}Đi mà! Đi mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:27.22,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{W-Well, in that case...}V-Vậy thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:33.23,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It was in the office kitchenette... \Nwhen we were alone...}Trong góc pha cà phê của văn phòng...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.23,0:08:34.94,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{The k-kitchenette?!}G-Góc pha cà phê?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.94,0:08:37.99,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I won't be able to keep me cool \Nnext time I'm in there!!}Lần tới sao mình dám đến đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:42.76,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I-I can't believe I said that! \NIt makes it sound like I'm setting him up!}S-Sao mình lại nói thế? Nghe cứ như đang mời gọi ấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:45.30,Main,Reporter,0,0,0,,{Okay, here's a question for the boyfriend.}Vậy đến bạn trai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:49.63,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I have to make sure I keep \NSenpai's premise going!}Mình phải tung hứng cùng chị ấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:53.62,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{But with my experience, there's gonna be \Nquestions I have no idea how to deal with,}Nhưng kinh nghiệm của mình... \Nsẽ không biết đối phó như nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.62,0:08:55.18,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\an8}{on top of being embarrassed...}Vì xấu hổ lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:57.39,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\b1\fscx120\fs28\c&H000000&\an6\bord0\shad0\fsp4\pos(229.334,166.667)}{Never had a\Ngirlfriend}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:56.90,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\an8}{What do I do?!}Làm sao đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.86,0:09:00.08,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I know!}Phải rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:02.34,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{What I learned at the new employee seminar!}Những gì mình học được ở buổi hướng dẫn lính mới.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.34,0:09:05.89,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{When you need to be flexible in your \Nthinking, pretend to be someone else!}Linh hoạt trong suy nghĩ, đặt bản thân vào người khác...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.32,0:09:07.71,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I'll be a playboy!}Mình sẽ là một dân chơi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.71,0:09:10.96,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{If I'm pretending to be a \Nplayer instead of myself,}Nếu giả vờ làm dân chơi thay vì bản thân,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.96,0:09:13.82,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I should be able to respond to \Nanything without freaking out!}mình sẽ trả lời mọi câu hỏi mà không sợ hãi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.21,0:09:17.15,Main,Yamagishi (M),0,0,0,,{Sup! Hell yeah, I get around! How }{\i1}{you}{\i0}{ doing?}Xin chào! Dân chơi đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.54,0:09:20.34,Main,Reporter,0,0,0,,{Let's start by hearing what you \Nlike about your girlfriend.}Vậy thì điểm bạn thích ở bạn gái là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:25.18,Main,Shinozazki,0,0,0,,{You wanna know about my current \Nsqueeze? Let me think...}Cô muốn biết về nó hả? Xem nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:27.58,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\b1\fscx120\fs20\c&H000000&\an5\bord0\shad0\pos(544,47.333)}{Possessed}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.98,0:09:27.59,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Sh-Shinozaki-san?!}S-Shinozaki
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.31,0:09:31.44,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Even being around her is awesome, y'know?}Bên cạnh cô ấy rất vui.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.44,0:09:34.08,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It's, like, a miracle we \Nhooked up, or something.}Cuộc gặp của bọn tôi như phép màu vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:36.85,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Sh-Sh-Sh-Shinozaki-san?!}S-S-Shinozaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:42.24,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{She's like a ninja with work time, too.}Và cô ấy làm việc như một nhẫn giả!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.24,0:09:45.86,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\an8}{The goddess who taught me there's something \Nsweeter than that OT pay, y'know?}Là nữ thần đã dạy tôi niềm vui\N trong công việc mỗi khi tăng ca.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:45.85,Italics,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,0)\fntimes new roman\b1\fscx120\fs20\c&H000000&\fsp4\an5\bord0\shad0\pos(320,345)}{Possessed, but still Shinozaki Inside}Giả vờ thôi chứ vẫn là Shinozaki
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:49.18,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{H-He's hugging me!}E-Em ấy ôm mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.18,0:09:53.97,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I guess... this is what Shinozaki-san \Nwould do with his girlfriend.}Có lẽ Shinozaki... sẽ làm thế này khi có bạn gái.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.97,0:09:56.99,Main,Reporter,0,0,0,,{So, what was your first time together like?}Vậy lần đầu của hai người thế nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:09:58.24,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{F-First—?!}L-Lần đầu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.53,0:10:01.00,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It was the second time she came by my place.}Là lần thứ 2 cô ấy đến nhà tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:03.99,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Th-The second—?!}L-Lần thứ 2?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.25,0:10:07.41,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{The first time would probably be \Ntoo much, even for a playboy...}Lần đầu thì hơi quá, ngay cả với một dân chơi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:12.18,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{The second time? I've been to \NShinozaki-san's house once before...}Lần thứ 2? Mình đã qua nhà em ấy 1 lần...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.18,0:10:15.50,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{D-Does that mean if I go again...}T-Tức là nếu lại đến...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.25,0:10:19.76,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-san, you left \Nsomething at the office.}Shinozaki, em để quên đồ nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:23.48,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{You came by a second time...}Chị đã đến lần thứ 2...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.67,0:10:27.03,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Do you know what that means, Senpai?}Chị hiểu rồi chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.03,0:10:29.05,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Sh-Shinozaki-san...}S-Shinozaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.39,0:10:33.17,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\an8}{W-We can't! It's still too soon!}C-Chúng ta vẫn còn quá sớm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.90,0:10:35.15,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,0)\fntimes new roman\b1\fscx120\fs20\c&H000000&\an4\bord0\shad0\pos(372,300)}{She forgot the basic premise\Nwas pretending to be dating\Nin the first place.}Quên mất đang diễn
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:40.44,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{For him to be able to say something \Nlike this without hesitation...}Em ấy có thể nói thế mà không lo lắng gì...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.44,0:10:42.41,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It's so shameless.}Thật bỉ ổi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:54.67,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I like how serious he is, and how he really \Nthrows himself into the tasks he's given.}Tôi thích cách anh ấy nghiêm túc\N và cố gắng trong công việc.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.11,0:10:58.16,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Oh, I see now...}À, ra là vậy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:11:05.44,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{He's throwing himself into answering this \Ninterview as seriously as possible.}Em ấy đang cố gắng hoàn thành cuộc phỏng vấn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.71,0:11:07.80,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-san, you truly are...}Shinozaki, em đúng là...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.44,0:11:11.19,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{a kohai I can be proud of.}đàn em mà chị tự hào.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:14.31,Main,Reporter,0,0,0,,{Let's end with a kiss!}Kết thúc bằng nụ hôn thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.56,0:11:19.70,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Uh, s-sure, piece of cake...}À vâng, dễ như ăn bánh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.25,0:11:22.12,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Crap, what now?!}Giờ sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:24.10,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{In that case...}Nếu thế thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.95,0:11:34.01,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{In that case, as his senpai, \NI need to support him.}Là một đàn chị, mình phải hỗ trợ em ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:36.50,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-san...}Shinozaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.20,0:11:39.67,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Don't push yourself too hard, okay?}Đừng cố gắng quá sức nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:42.64,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{O-Okay.}V-Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:46.27,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Does that work?}Thế nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.27,0:11:50.16,Main,Reprter,0,0,0,,{Perfect! Thank you so much for this!}Tuyệt vời, xin cảm ơn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.16,0:11:54.03,Main,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{Are these two seriously not dating...?}Cả hai... không hẹn hò hả?
