Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.30,0:12:49.90,Main,President,0,0,0,,{You've all worked hard again this year.}Năm nay chúng ta đã chăm chỉ làm việc.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.51,0:12:53.57,Main,President,0,0,0,,{I want you all to enjoy yourselves.}Tôi muốn các bạn hãy tận hưởng!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.57,0:12:55.75,Main,President,0,0,0,,{After all, it's Christmas!}Vì hôm nay là giáng sinh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:13:00.18,Main,President,0,0,0,,{Let's drink to our future success, \Nand to Santa's generosity!}Hãy uống vì tương lai công ty\Nvà sự hào phóng của Santa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:02.41,Main,President,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:03.91,Main,President,0,0,0,,{Cheers!}Cạn ly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.91,0:13:05.30,Main,Workers,0,0,0,,{Cheers!}Cạn ly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:10.80,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Oh, Shinozaki-kun, \Nyou're such a Shinozaki-kun....}Shinozaki thiệt là...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.80,0:13:11.94,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Is it true?}Thật ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.94,0:13:13.32,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Of course not!}Không có đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:19.05,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai!}Chị ơi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.30,0:13:22.02,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Are you heading home?}Chị đang về hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.02,0:13:25.31,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I am, too, so why don't we walk \Nto the station together?}Em cũng về nữa, đi cùng nhau đến ga nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:27.90,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Sure.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.84,0:13:35.50,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{The party was a lot of fun.}Buổi tiệc vui nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:38.19,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{The food was delicious, too.}Thức ăn cũng ngon nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.19,0:13:38.83,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{And then...}Và...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.43,0:13:41.06,Flashback,Akina,0,0,0,,{I'm Santa! Ho, ho, ho!}Tôi là santa đây! Ho ho ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:44.80,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{We got to see a rare managerial Santa.}Còn được gặp ông già noel nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:47.33,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{He was really enjoying himself!}Anh ấy cũng tận hưởng ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.15,0:13:50.09,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Maybe Senpai will dress \Nlike Santa next year...}Có khi năm sau chị ấy sẽ mặc...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.88,0:13:52.87,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.99,0:13:56.10,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Glorious...}Quá đã...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.33,0:13:59.51,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{The whole city's really \Nin Christmas mode, huh?}Cả thành phố ngập tràn trong lễ hội nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.51,0:14:01.06,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{S-Sure is.}V-Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.06,0:14:03.53,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-san, do you have any plans?}Shinozaki nè, em có kế hoạch gì nữa không?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:05.02,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Not really.}Không ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.43,0:14:07.37,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{In that case...}Vậy thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.92,0:14:11.46,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{since it's a special occasion, shall we \Ngo somewhere before heading home?}vì là dịp đặc biệt nên ghé đâu đó không?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.36,0:14:16.27,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:19.21,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{What do you think, Shinozaki-san?}Em thấy sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.20,0:14:22.29,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Let's head there next!}Tiếp theo là bên kia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:22.88,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Sure!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.24,0:14:24.34,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It's so soothing...}Thật mềm mại...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:26.00,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Incredibly cute.}Dễ thương quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.57,0:14:32.01,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Wh-Whoa... Incredible.}T-Tuyệt ghê...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.01,0:14:33.58,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It's so beautiful.}Đẹp quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:37.94,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{This tree's famous, apparently...}Gần đây nó đang nổi lắm đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:43.41,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I've been meaning to visit it for a while, \Nbut the chance never really came up.}Chị đã định đến mấy lần rồi mà chưa có cơ hội.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:49.90,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I'm glad we got to see it \Ntogether, Shinozaki-san.}Thật tuyệt khi được đi cùng em.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:53.91,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Me, too.}Em cũng thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:59.58,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I'm really happy to spend Christmas \Nwith you like this, Senpai.}Em thực sự rất vui khi được tận \Nhưởng giáng sinh cùng chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.16,0:15:05.30,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{S-So embarrassing...}X-Xấu hổ quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:09.16,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Wh-Where do you suppose Santa \Nis flying right about now?}Em nghĩ bây giờ ông già noel đang ở đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.16,0:15:13.82,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It must be really hard delivering presents \Nto kids around the world in one night.}Đi phát quà khắp thế giới chắc vất vả lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.82,0:15:15.36,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{True enough...}Phải nhỉ...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.96,0:15:21.55,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Are there any presents you got from \NSanta that you remember, Shinozaki-san?}Em còn nhớ mình được ông\Ngià noel tặng quà gì không?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.84,0:15:23.03,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Presents...}Quà...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.39,0:15:27.31,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Let me think... There was \Na video game I wanted once,}Hình như... có một lần em nhận\N được game mình muốn...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.04,0:15:30.85,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{but then I got the wrong one.}nhưng mở ra lại là loại khác.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:35.36,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{But since it was from Santa, \NI tried to enjoy it...}Nhưng là quà của ông già noel nên em chơi luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:39.87,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{and by the time I was done, \Nit had really grown on me.}Và khi hoàn thành nó thì em cũng trưởng thành.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.47,0:15:45.33,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{You were a sweetheart when \Nyou were little, too, I see.}Em hồi nhỏ đúng là tốt bụng nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.33,0:15:47.55,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Y-You think...?}V-Vậy sao...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:50.24,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{What about you, Senpai?}Còn chị?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:51.85,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Let me think...}Xem nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.65,0:15:58.73,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{One time, I got this cute stuffed cat, \Nand I wanted to have it with me all the time.}Có một lần chị được tặng bé mèo\N nhồi bông dễ thương nên ôm theo suốt...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.25,0:16:04.14,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I ended up taking it to kindergarten, \Nand my parents received a call about it.}Thậm chí mang đến cả trường\N tiểu học và làm phiền ba mẹ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.05,0:16:07.98,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{That's adorable.}Dễ thương ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:09.73,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{And definitely sounds like you.}Và đúng là kiểu của chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.48,0:16:14.88,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I guess we haven't changed \Nmuch since we were little.}Có vẻ chúng ta không thay đổi là mấy nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:25.12,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I guess staying out for so long, \Nit was bound to get cold.}Ở ngoài lâu quá nên lạnh ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.37,0:16:28.88,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai! She doesn't have gloves!}Chị ấy không có găng tay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.29,0:16:33.12,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Maybe I should subtly guide \Nher hands into my pockets...?}Lúc này mình sẽ lấy tay chị ấy và cho túi áo mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:36.64,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{What a good kohai you are! It's so warm!}Đúng là đàn em của chị! Ấm ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.13,0:16:41.42,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{That might be kinda rude, though, \Nso I should ask first...}Nhưng thô lỗ lắm, hỏi trước cho chắc.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.42,0:16:43.16,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Uh, Senpai...}Chị ơi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.51,0:16:46.30,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{She had gloves!}Chị ấy có mang găng kìa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.16,0:16:48.52,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{What's wrong?}Sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:52.70,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Uh, well... nothing, really.}À không có gì ạ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:57.16,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Huh? Shinozaki-san, \Ndo you not have any gloves?}Shinozaki, em không có găng tay à?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:58.95,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Oh, no.}À vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:02.12,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{But I'll be okay with \Nmy hands in my pockets.}Nhưng em bỏ tay vào túi là ổn rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:05.67,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{That's no good! I've got extras, so here...}Không được! Chị còn một đôi nữa nên...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.91,0:17:08.54,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Yeah, that makes sense.}Phải rồi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:13.98,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I'm so sorry! I'll make sure \Nto have some ready next year.}Xin lỗi nhé! Chị sẽ chuẩn bị tốt cho năm sau.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.98,0:17:17.46,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{No, I should probably just \Nget some of my own...}Không không, phải là em chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:20.92,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{She just casually made a \Npromise for next year.}Chị ấy vừa hứa sang năm sẽ tặng găng tay kìa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.92,0:17:23.57,Main,Man A,0,0,0,,{Ugh, look at this.}Nhìn kìa. Biết ngay mà, 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.57,0:17:25.45,Main,Man A,0,0,0,,{Just like I figured, \Nwe came at the worst time.}giờ này đúng là tệ nhất mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.45,0:17:28.31,Main,Man B,0,0,0,,{Tell me about it. \NCouples, as far as the eye can see!}Đúng đó, đi đâu cũng toàn cặp đôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:30.25,Main,Man A,0,0,0,,{What a drag...}Thiệt tình...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.87,0:17:33.02,Main,Man A,0,0,0,,{Will springtime ever come for us?}Khi nào mới đến chúng ta?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.02,0:17:36.71,Main,Man B,0,0,0,,{I bet everyone here is gonna \Nhave a great time later on.}Ở đây ai cũng có vẻ hạnh phúc nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:40.41,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Um, perhaps we should head on home?}C-Chúng ta nên về thôi ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:42.45,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{G-Good idea.}À ừm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:45.20,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Oh, but first...}Cơ mà trước đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.86,0:17:46.73,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Here.}Đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.07,0:17:48.70,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{The bear loungewear?}Là bộ đồ ngủ gấu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:52.97,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{When we were heading back from that meeting, \Nwe both thought they looked nice, right?}Khi quay về sau cuộc họp, chúng ta đã ngắm nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.97,0:17:55.70,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It's a Christmas present from your senpai.}Là quà Giáng sinh của đàn chị đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:57.96,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Do you like it?}Em có thích không?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.96,0:18:00.84,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I-I do! Thank you!}E-Em có! Cảm ơn chị!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:02.21,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{And to be honest...}Và thực ra...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.34,0:18:05.68,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It's the rabbit one, from the same time.}Là bộ đồ thỏ lúc đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.07,0:18:09.86,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Thank you so much!}Cảm ơn em.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.33,0:18:12.87,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I guess we were thinking the same thing...}Chúng ta nghĩ giống nhau ghê...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:16.62,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Something about that makes me happy.}Nhưng nó làm chị vui lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.62,0:18:22.12,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I thought you would look good \Nin it, and how I'd like to see that...}Em đã nghĩ chị mặc nó sẽ hợp lắm nên là...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.26,0:18:28.75,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{W-Well, since we traded \Npresents, let's hurry home!}Đ-Đổi quà xong rồi thì nhanh về thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.30,0:18:31.25,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{We could...}Chúng ta có thể...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.27,0:18:37.30,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{We could... show each other...}có thể... cho nhau xem...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:39.52,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Wait... you mean...}Tức là...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:41.31,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{that...}chuyện đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.47,0:18:53.95,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Can't believe I left the flash on!}Không thể tin là anh quên tắt flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.95,0:18:55.58,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{I'll regret this until the day I die.}Anh sẽ hối hận đến ngày mình chết!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.58,0:18:56.98,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Seriously!}Thiệt tình...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.98,0:18:57.97,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Manager?!}Quản lý?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:18:59.49,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Hayakawa-san, too?!}Cả Hayakawa nữa sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.82,0:19:03.23,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Unbelievable! How long have \Nyou two been watching?!}Không thể tin nổi! Hai người ở đó từ khi nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:06.35,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Well, it was very sweet!}Chà, ngọt ngào ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:09.70,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Sweeter than any Christmas \Nor fruitcake I've ever had!}Còn ngọt hơn cả bánh giáng sinh mà tôi từng ăn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.70,0:19:14.76,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I have to say, Katase-san, you're bolder\N than I figured. I'm surprised.}Cơ mà chị bạo dạn hơn em nghĩ đó chị Katase.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:20.79,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I mean, considering you discussing showing \Neach other loungewear on Christmas Day...}Tặng nhau cả quần áo ngủ vào ngày lễ Giáng sinh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:30.03,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{N-N-No! Not that! I thought we could send \Neach other pictures of us wearing them!}K-K-Không phải! Chị chỉ nghĩ hai đứa\N mặc vào xong chụp ảnh trao đổi thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.03,0:19:33.59,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{And then... uh... well...}Sau đó... thì là...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.60,0:19:39.03,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{We could... exchange contact info, maybe...}Có thể... trao đổi thông tin liên lạc...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.04,0:19:44.46,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Oh, right! Let's do that!}Vâng! Làm thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.46,0:19:45.78,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Exchange contact info!}Trao đổi thông tin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:48.15,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Th-Thank you...}Mong em giúp đỡ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.15,0:19:49.00,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{R-Right!}V-Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:50.97,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{You, too, Hayakawa-san.}Em nữa Hayakawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.97,0:19:53.05,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Uh, err, I'm good.}E-Em ổn mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.76,0:19:59.04,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{O-Okay, fine!}E-Em hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:00.80,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Xong rồi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:02.42,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Thank you, Hayakawa-san!}Cảm ơn em.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.71,0:20:05.96,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It's snowing.}Tuyết kìa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:11.11,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It's a white Christmas. How romantic.}Là giáng sinh trắng, lãng mạn ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.11,0:20:12.08,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.08,0:20:13.95,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Almost seems too convenient.}Cứ như đang ủng hộ vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.95,0:20:17.85,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Let's chalk it up to God bestowing a \Nblessing on hard-working people.}Chúa ban phước lành cho \Nnhững nhân viên chăm chỉ mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.06,0:20:20.71,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{That sounds right!}Đúng thế nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.49,0:20:23.41,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Do you think the \Nsnow will pile up?}Không biết có rơi nhiều không?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.41,0:20:25.18,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{That'd be nice.}Nếu thế thì tuyệt lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:27.48,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{And then we can all \Nmake a snowman together!}Và chúng ta có thể làm người tuyết.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.13,0:20:29.45,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I like that idea!}Em thích ý tưởng đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:30.06,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I dunno...}Em thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.06,0:20:31.67,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{What kind of ears would \Nyou want, Hayakawa-san?}Em thích đeo loại tai nào, Hayakawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.67,0:20:33.24,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Why are we talking about ears?}Sao lại nói về tai?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.92,0:20:44.85,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Okay!}Rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:55.14,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{So short...}Ngắn quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.14,0:20:58.44,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Maybe I'm a little too old \Nfor this kind of thing?}Mình quá già để mặc nó rồi nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.76,0:21:03.15,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{But it's loungewear, so... \Nit's probably fine.}Nhưng đồ ngủ mà, không sao cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:05.41,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Besides, it was a gift!}Với cả quà tặng nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.48,0:21:12.40,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{How's it look?}H-Hợp không?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.36,0:21:17.43,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I shouldn't expect an \Nanswer from a plushie...}Mình không nghĩ nó có thể trả lời...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:23.67,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{But, I think... Shinozaki-san...}Nhưng mà... nếu là Shinozaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:30.65,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Thank you.}Cảm ơn em.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.22,0:21:50.10,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{Bleary-eyed and not fully awake from a dream}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:55.00,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{I still can't bring myself \Nto drink that bitter coffee}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.56,0:21:59.48,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{So I sneakily toss in \Ntwo pinches of a sweet secret}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.48,0:22:03.70,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{And let it slowly spread throughout}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.92,0:22:08.66,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{There's a local bakery \Nthat's only open sometimes}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.66,0:22:13.55,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{Where I once had some toast that glittered}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.21,0:22:18.05,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{What is it that makes it so satisfying?}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.05,0:22:22.22,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{Almost like magic}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.64,0:22:27.30,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{I find myself thinking about that kind of thing}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.30,0:22:32.99,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{How the small things can be the most precious}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.75,0:22:37.70,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{Deep inside my heart}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.70,0:22:42.10,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{It's ever so bittersweet}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.97,0:22:47.09,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{"Just being around you is enough"}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.09,0:22:51.04,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{Becomes my mantra}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.04,0:22:53.33,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{Baby like sugar}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.52,0:23:02.66,Italics - Top,,0,0,0,,{Baby you're the sugar}
